{"tid":1561892,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"18區集合．九龍塘大合唱","createTime":"2019-09-11T18:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:45:10.000Z","uid":222817,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b57fc65784c92631fe80dc1619b919676754a7be","tid":1561892,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:58:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要人啊！全世界今晚同我入嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srMAjaD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrMAjaD.png&h=fd855eef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日得小弟我自己一個喺又一城嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等咗三個字都冇人嗌口號 結果小弟嗌咗兩聲都冇人應<br />\n跟住老尷得濟走咗了。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JZigZK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JZigZK.png&h=25233aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你睇下其他區 九龍塘呢？？<br />\n你哋肯出嚟未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你諗下 九龍塘一直都好似與世隔絕咗咁 如果我哋<span style=\"color: red;\">喺個中產社區入手慢慢叫醒佢哋</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBu city 各位大大唔該幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊喺又一城光復香港！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6YCxzR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH6YCxzR.png&h=8437001c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdWwB1C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdWwB1C.png&h=69d6eb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n．九龍塘都有連儂橋㗎！大家幫幫手今晩入又一城orzzz <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港時代革命<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚九點啊！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b223738f487dcf067d3d52b59dadb892888cf693","tid":1561892,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9926185e91cc7c647d66d23ff6067d937f28b61f","tid":1561892,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:58:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"623d7f4c262fead1ef278a46eb25e3bffefa08a1","tid":1561892,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f6d6cb811faf98e5adeaf74cd9a7e5136cb294e8","tid":1561892,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:59:00.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"cdc4bbe4971eba7ae8b121d79b0c1f19ecce5b4f","tid":1561892,"uid":222817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T18:59:10.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"1aabb9f8a7effc4853e9be81cd3d5c4a548927e5","tid":1561892,"uid":222817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEuRB23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEuRB23.jpg&h=3b08dbf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7FZY1uK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih